WEBVTT

00:00:31.182 --> 00:00:36.449
Today is a special day, called as Akshaya Tritiya.

00:00:36.543 --> 00:00:47.250
Akshaya means something that cannot be
destroyed, cannot be changed, that cannot be challenged,

00:00:47.337 --> 00:00:52.176
and that is the third day of the moon which is tritiya.

00:00:53.357 --> 00:00:58.302
It is regarded as the best day to decide,

00:00:58.389 --> 00:01:05.095
to decide to do something or to have some sort of a determination.

00:01:05.176 --> 00:01:08.648
This determination is such which will never change,

00:01:08.728 --> 00:01:13.829
which will never [unclear] which will not have problems.

00:01:13.910 --> 00:01:17.526
That’s what it means; today is the day, it’s very important,

00:01:17.625 --> 00:01:26.599
that we should decide as to something which is very, very firm, which will never be faded.

00:01:26.679 --> 00:01:33.468
It’s a very important day and that’s why the
Indian people, when they want to take up something,

00:01:33.549 --> 00:01:39.541
some sort of a challenge, some sort of a precedent,
then they decide on this day

00:01:39.621 --> 00:01:42.902
that: I will do this

00:01:42.987 --> 00:01:50.910
And this decision will be absolutely indestructible, will never be challenged.

00:01:51.022 --> 00:01:59.216
It’s a very good day because we have sometimes 
so many problems, and we want to overcome them

00:01:59.309 --> 00:02:06.294
At that time, when sometimes our weaknesses, sometimes our tendencies try to

00:02:06.374 --> 00:02:09.923
– after all, we are human beings, so they try to

00:02:10.004 --> 00:02:15.746
neutralise, or sometimes try to take us away from reality

00:02:15.826 --> 00:02:19.608
But once on that day you decide for something good

00:02:19.688 --> 00:02:29.149
– to do something, to accept something – that should be absolutely, firmly adhered to.

00:02:29.229 --> 00:02:35.041
It’s a very good day that we should really stick on.

00:02:35.668 --> 00:02:40.148
So for Sahaja Yogis, what have we to decide?

00:02:40.228 --> 00:02:45.485
That is to be seen today what we can decide to do.

00:02:45.591 --> 00:02:57.459
Now there are many, we should say, many
reactions, permutations on our way, as Sahaj Yogis also,

00:02:57.546 --> 00:03:02.469
because you have now become one with the all-pervading Power of divine love.

00:03:02.549 --> 00:03:13.728
And when you have become that, you are the
person who is just one with that great Power of God,

00:03:13.815 --> 00:03:24.981
then you have to decide firstly, that you will always remain connected
with that Power, always;

00:03:25.062 --> 00:03:29.822
that is the supreme Power, that is the Power
that [unclear/controls everything],

00:03:29.907 --> 00:03:32.809
and that is the Power of love.

00:03:33.416 --> 00:03:40.275
So, we have to decide that whatever we do, whatever we are trying to achieve,

00:03:40.374 --> 00:03:44.910
whatever we are trying to make in life begins through love,

00:03:44.990 --> 00:03:50.797
that gives this determination and this faith should be with you.

00:03:50.878 --> 00:03:57.164
Through love only we can do, not through hatred, not through violence, not through anger.

00:03:57.274 --> 00:03:59.996
Many people believe that it’s not possible,

00:04:00.076 --> 00:04:05.022
but I personally feel that this Power is the most powerful thing

00:04:05.102 --> 00:04:12.164
and it is such a, such a energy that it acts.

00:04:12.245 --> 00:04:16.843
It has computer of its own, I should say; it works so beautifully.

00:04:16.923 --> 00:04:24.923
If you desire for anything, if you ask for anything, 
you see if it’s a pure desire, it works.

00:04:25.004 --> 00:04:30.134
So we have to depend on this Power of all-pervading Power of divine love.

00:04:30.215 --> 00:04:39.446
And with this love what do we get? We get a kind of an assurance all the time.

00:04:39.527 --> 00:04:43.777
Now many people tell Me: this miracle took place, that miracle took place,

00:04:43.858 --> 00:04:46.298
this happened, this has worked.

00:04:46.379 --> 00:04:48.408
So many people tell Me.

00:04:48.488 --> 00:04:55.012
But the main thing behind all of this is this Power that is working it out.

00:04:55.093 --> 00:05:01.865
It works all the time and it is so competent, it is so fast that,

00:05:01.945 --> 00:05:04.871
we don’t have to worry about anything.

00:05:04.952 --> 00:05:10.131
But one thing should be that our desire should be pure.

00:05:10.841 --> 00:05:16.630
Now what is the pure desire in this, this desire of God Almighty?

00:05:16.710 --> 00:05:19.940
He has created this universe, He created this world,

00:05:20.020 --> 00:05:29.533
He created us with the desire to create a beautiful vision of His own.

00:05:29.614 --> 00:05:34.869
What is His vision is that we should always, all of us, be very happy.

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:38.270
The other day I told in My lecture, as you have heard,

00:05:38.357 --> 00:05:44.651
that every human being has a Kundalini – that’s the Mother that you
have –

00:05:44.731 --> 00:05:49.549
and everybody’s Kundalini acts the same way, behaves the same way.

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:54.466
So to believe that we are different people is wrong; we are all one.

00:05:54.547 --> 00:05:58.105
But those who believe we are different can be violent,

00:05:58.186 --> 00:06:01.952
can be very aggressive: can be very destructive also.

00:06:02.033 --> 00:06:09.283
But with this Power, you can overcome and let them understand that it’s all wrong.

00:06:09.364 --> 00:06:14.262
We are all one people created by God, we are all in the same pattern,

00:06:14.349 --> 00:06:18.328
with the same Kundalini, which acts the same way.

00:06:18.409 --> 00:06:22.762
Now, if you realise that we are all one

00:06:22.842 --> 00:06:28.701
and if you understand that we are guided by one Power,

00:06:28.787 --> 00:06:32.179
you will be amazed how peaceful you will be.

00:06:32.260 --> 00:06:36.054
All the things are happening in this world just as a drama,

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:39.451
and you should see it as a drama, the whole thing,

00:06:39.531 --> 00:06:46.133
and you will be amazed how your desires and your visions will be fulfilled.

00:06:46.213 --> 00:06:53.354
Very clearly you will see that and you will be really so much surprised

00:06:53.434 --> 00:07:02.328
at the whole happening, at the whole becoming, the whole… just appearing before you.

00:07:02.408 --> 00:07:07.727
Suddenly you will find everything works out the way you like.

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:22.537
This is the day, which is very important I think for everyone,

00:07:22.617 --> 00:07:30.118
which is promised that, this day or yesterday and whenever you decide

00:07:30.198 --> 00:07:35.871
that, I will have the use of this divine Power

00:07:35.951 --> 00:07:43.049
for all the purposes that Almighty desires, will just work.

00:07:43.136 --> 00:07:53.375
It will work in such a beautiful manner that you will be amazed 
how these things happen suddenly.

00:07:53.460 --> 00:08:00.958
The other day I met a lady and she told Me of lots of miracles that have happened;

00:08:01.038 --> 00:08:08.508
how she was ill, how she could not get work, 
how the burglars came in her house and ran away.

00:08:08.589 --> 00:08:16.306
Apart from that, how her little girl, her child [unclear] 
and all kinds of things she told Me.

00:08:16.393 --> 00:08:23.633
So I listened to her, because [unclear] so many things there are.

00:08:23.714 --> 00:08:26.769
But then I asked her, ‘What do you think of this, first of all,

00:08:26.863 --> 00:08:31.230
that you have so many miracles compared to other Sahaja Yogis.

00:08:31.317 --> 00:08:36.442
What is so special?’ She said, ‘Mother, I don’t know how.

00:08:36.523 --> 00:08:39.688
But I have got a lot of shraddha.’.

00:08:39.775 --> 00:08:44.238
Shraddha is devotion, devotion without question,

00:08:44.325 --> 00:08:53.337
is that inner growth within yourself where you become so much dedicated,

00:08:53.418 --> 00:09:02.042
you enjoy your dedication and enjoy yourself also, the way you are dedicated.

00:09:02.123 --> 00:09:04.410
This dedication has worked out

00:09:04.490 --> 00:09:13.551
and this dedication has brought to her all these beautiful experiences in life,

00:09:13.631 --> 00:09:18.211
and I really thought that must be the reason – shraddha.

00:09:18.292 --> 00:09:23.888
She said, ‘Only the shraddha that, I can say that I have.’

00:09:23.969 --> 00:09:28.401
And I find out some Sahaja Yogis, they don’t have so much shraddha.

00:09:28.482 --> 00:09:34.138
But some have so much of inner shraddhas that they have told Me that:

00:09:34.219 --> 00:09:41.747
‘Miracle has lost its meaning, it has lost its existence: 
is just for us, has
become a natural.’

00:09:41.828 --> 00:09:48.044
So, this shraddha has to be seen that it grows within you.

00:09:48.145 --> 00:09:53.828
Now you cannot make it grow like you make things and all that.

00:09:53.915 --> 00:09:56.476
That’s not artificial, it’s real.

00:09:56.557 --> 00:10:04.410
It’s a real thing which is inborn within you, within us, like a little plant it grows.

00:10:04.491 --> 00:10:10.045
It grows and grows and grows by itself, through the living process.

00:10:10.126 --> 00:10:12.773
In the same way this also grows.

00:10:12.854 --> 00:10:18.579
But what do you do with it? How to make it grow is with your love.

00:10:18.660 --> 00:10:23.814
You have to respect yourself, you have to love yourself

00:10:23.900 --> 00:10:28.882
and you have to understand that this body is meant for God’s work

00:10:28.962 --> 00:10:34.940
and once you start looking after your body and looking after yourself

00:10:35.052 --> 00:10:42.681
in a way that is divine, then it is shraddha, grows just like a plant can grow.

00:10:42.769 --> 00:10:48.376
But it is a living process and what water you have to give within is that of love.

00:10:48.457 --> 00:10:51.710
So to love yourself doesn’t mean to be selfish.

00:10:51.797 --> 00:10:56.728
It by no means it means to be something very special.

00:10:56.809 --> 00:11:04.359
To love yourself is first of all that you should not 
allow many of these things to touch you.

00:11:04.453 --> 00:11:07.029
One of them is ego.

00:11:07.110 --> 00:11:10.049
If ego is there then you don’t love yourself;

00:11:10.129 --> 00:11:13.099
you love your ego which can be dangerous,

00:11:13.179 --> 00:11:17.451
which can be polluted and which can be just very aggressive.

00:11:18.243 --> 00:11:24.073
While if you love yourself, then you don’t have ego.

00:11:24.154 --> 00:11:26.713
You just laugh at yourself sometimes,

00:11:26.793 --> 00:11:34.221
how it behaves, [unclear] in the company of ego, 
and you try to just get out of this.

00:11:34.302 --> 00:11:39.111
I have seen many people in Sahaja Yoga, 
once they are in Sahaja Yoga,

00:11:39.202 --> 00:11:43.979
they say, ‘Mother if we do like this, will our ego grow?’

00:11:44.059 --> 00:11:49.581
I said, ‘No, it won’t.’ Don’t have these feelings that, 
if your ego will grow.

00:11:49.669 --> 00:11:55.889
But you should know one thing for definite that, 
when ego comes, you’ll behave in a manner

00:11:55.969 --> 00:12:01.373
which will take away your vibrations, 
which will take away whatever you have now.

00:12:01.454 --> 00:12:07.513
And you know it is so good that you can also 
judge yourself through your vibrations.

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:10.205
On your fingertips you will know what you are catching

00:12:10.286 --> 00:12:13.119
and you are not ashamed to accept that.

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:15.507
I have seen many people coming and telling Me,

00:12:15.587 --> 00:12:19.933
‘Mother, you know my ego is catching, will You take it out? 
I am too much of egotistical.’

00:12:20.025 --> 00:12:24.486
You see, anybody who says that can see himself, can see that;

00:12:24.567 --> 00:12:30.468
it is very clear that he can see himself that this was their ego working.

00:12:30.549 --> 00:12:35.309
There are, as they say, there are six enemies you have

00:12:35.389 --> 00:12:42.740
and all these six enemies can drop out without 
any difficulty once you start loving yourself.

00:12:42.852 --> 00:12:48.132
If you are in love with anything, you wouldn’t accept anything wrong, anything…

00:12:49.248 --> 00:12:57.383
this feeling or that, or some other bad thing; you would like to keep it clean.

00:12:57.464 --> 00:13:01.278
So when you love yourself, you try to keep yourself clean.

00:13:01.359 --> 00:13:07.097
Clean means absolutely saaf, which is sufi, that they call: Sufi is saaf.

00:13:07.177 --> 00:13:09.403
So you become clean, you become nirmal.

00:13:09.483 --> 00:13:15.571
And that’s what is you have to do if you really love yourself and care for yourself.

00:13:15.652 --> 00:13:20.296
So on this day you have to decide that, first of all for yourself,

00:13:20.389 --> 00:13:24.960
you have to ask that you should be clean,

00:13:25.046 --> 00:13:30.081
you should be absolutely devoid of all the six enemies.

00:13:30.169 --> 00:13:34.651
Then for others, you have to think of their well-being,

00:13:34.737 --> 00:13:37.621
by saying that they should also become Sahaja Yogis.

00:13:37.702 --> 00:13:42.442
Why not? We have entered into the Kingdom of God, why not get others also.

00:13:42.523 --> 00:13:45.521
Talk to them about it. Manage somehow or other.

00:13:45.602 --> 00:13:48.755
You can raise Kundalini of all other people

00:13:48.835 --> 00:13:52.835
and you can make them one with this all-pervading Power

00:13:52.921 --> 00:13:55.591
where there is no discretion, there’s nothing,

00:13:55.677 --> 00:14:01.662
and you become absolutely a clean personality with other people being helped.

00:14:01.742 --> 00:14:05.882
And it’s such a joy-giving thing to give realisations to others.

00:14:05.963 --> 00:14:09.633
So whenever you have a chance, you must try to do it.

00:14:09.714 --> 00:14:14.476
Something that I must tell you that, this love is also universal.

00:14:14.557 --> 00:14:20.437
I have seen people from Germany especially, who were supposed to be tough people.

00:14:20.517 --> 00:14:24.586
Most of their forefathers had killed so many people

00:14:24.693 --> 00:14:30.079
and they are going to all of the places wherever they think they have done something wrong

00:14:30.159 --> 00:14:33.506
and I was asking them,‘Why are you here?’

00:14:33.592 --> 00:14:37.288
They said, ‘Mother, don’t You think we have to do something bigger,

00:14:37.381 --> 00:14:43.940
because our forefathers have been cruel to these people, so we have to correct it.’

00:14:44.021 --> 00:14:51.642
See like this, a kind of a feeling comes in
that shows that, also your forefathers did all this:

00:14:51.729 --> 00:14:57.545
‘So we are responsible now, we should try to neutralise it and to make it different.’.

00:14:57.625 --> 00:15:01.966
So this love for [unclear] the whole being,within and without.

00:15:02.054 --> 00:15:06.063
When you see a person, this love gives you a great strength,

00:15:06.156 --> 00:15:09.936
and a great strength to fight all kinds of odds, I’ll tell you.

00:15:10.023 --> 00:15:14.173
Because you’ll become a silent person: start watching everybody.

00:15:14.254 --> 00:15:20.581
Only with that kind of a personality you can fight the evil of the world, otherwise not.

00:15:20.662 --> 00:15:27.363
If you are angry, with violence, or try to overpower others, you cannot,

00:15:27.475 --> 00:15:32.607
because you yourself have taken all the bad things of the other person.

00:15:32.694 --> 00:15:35.860
So the only attribute should be of love,

00:15:35.946 --> 00:15:39.854
and see a person with love and this will help clear out,

00:15:39.935 --> 00:15:49.260
and this is what is today’s great – I should say, 
a great effect of the divine Power of love.

00:15:49.341 --> 00:15:54.814
Whatever has to be done will be done by this Power: you leave it to this, it will do it.

00:15:54.902 --> 00:16:01.128
If you don’t leave it, then what happens,
that it says: ‘All right, you want to try it: try.’

00:16:01.209 --> 00:16:04.306
In Marathi, they say: [sounds like/ Al kol arisht kubai’];

00:16:04.386 --> 00:16:08.495
All right, you have some special connect, all right, you
have that:

00:16:08.587 --> 00:16:12.620
then work it out; and it will allow you to work it out. And you will never work it out.

00:16:12.700 --> 00:16:16.258
But if you say: ‘All right, I am not going to work it out, you work it out.

00:16:16.338 --> 00:16:20.265
I have nothing to do with it, you do it. You make everything work,

00:16:20.345 --> 00:16:27.476
so quick, so beautifully, and so marvellously, you should be amazed how it has worked out.

00:16:27.557 --> 00:16:32.053
The basic problem is that we don’t understand sometimes,

00:16:32.133 --> 00:16:36.952
we don’t realise how powerful is this Power.

00:16:37.033 --> 00:16:43.082
It thinks, it understands, it organises, it cares for you.

00:16:43.163 --> 00:16:45.798
Above all it loves you.

00:16:45.898 --> 00:16:55.469
If you can be one with it, you’ll become so sensitive and so much knowledgeable about it.

00:16:55.569 --> 00:17:00.987
And it gives you that powers we call as [unclear] – cognitive science, they say.

00:17:01.068 --> 00:17:06.134
But I would say, the science beyond the sciences, the science beyond your mind.

00:17:06.215 --> 00:17:11.872
And once you have that within you, you will immediately know whatever it knows.

00:17:11.953 --> 00:17:15.652
And the best part of it is, it is most practical, most practical.

00:17:15.733 --> 00:17:18.305
It gives you ideas the most practical.

00:17:18.385 --> 00:17:23.921
I am telling you; you will be amazed to say that, 
‘Mother, Sahaja Yoga is very practical.’.

00:17:24.007 --> 00:17:29.679
It is the Power which you have to realise and know and to have faith in it

00:17:29.759 --> 00:17:34.708
that, you have created the shraddha, 
[unclear/ that is the Power that’s going to work out.].

00:17:34.788 --> 00:17:36.354
You can call it by any name.

00:17:36.434 --> 00:17:42.886
You can call it by Paramchaitanya, all-pervading Power of God, or divine love.

00:17:42.973 --> 00:17:44.520
You can call it as Ruh.

00:17:44.601 --> 00:17:50.038
You can call it as Brahmachaitanya – all kinds of things have been written.

00:17:50.118 --> 00:17:55.711
But the main thing is whatever may be the name, it is a Power

00:17:55.804 --> 00:18:00.099
which is so all-pervading, which has created all this world, everything,

00:18:00.179 --> 00:18:02.952
it has created us; it has evolved us.

00:18:03.033 --> 00:18:07.448
Now at this juncture, the time has come for you to feel it.

00:18:07.528 --> 00:18:12.804
You feel it, and you can feel it all around and it’s so joy-giving.

00:18:12.885 --> 00:18:14.384
It’s so joy-giving.

00:18:14.465 --> 00:18:16.992
So we are not bothered for what others are doing,

00:18:17.072 --> 00:18:21.002
what others are creating: more problems they are doing.

00:18:21.082 --> 00:18:29.639
You leave it to this Power, to this Power which is so powerful, so beautiful and so right.

00:18:29.720 --> 00:18:35.274
So today is the day when we have to decide that, I leave everything to this Power.

00:18:35.355 --> 00:18:41.564
Let us see what it [unclear/has done.] Few people, even if you desire, it will work.

00:18:41.645 --> 00:18:46.577
It is quite a powerful thing and if you will only ask [unclear/it for it,] it will work.

00:18:46.657 --> 00:18:52.169
And whatever is good for whatever country, for our world, for human beings,

00:18:52.249 --> 00:18:55.196
it just works out very smoothly.

00:18:55.276 --> 00:19:01.716
You shouldn’t try to expedite it, you shouldn’t try to force it, because it knows.

00:19:01.797 --> 00:19:04.977
It knows how it has to – you see, it is [unclear.]

00:19:05.057 --> 00:19:15.216
You see for example, if you watch a little seed, when it sprouts, how the roots go down.

00:19:15.302 --> 00:19:22.009
Little root, you know, goes down and down and then it hits the obstruction of a stone.

00:19:22.090 --> 00:19:25.581
Where does it go? Round; it goes around the stone,

00:19:25.667 --> 00:19:31.206
so that the stone can be [unclear/ used for its later purpose.]

00:19:31.286 --> 00:19:34.949
Then it will go again round and round, up to a point

00:19:35.029 --> 00:19:39.366
where it has to go to stabilise: stabilise that root.

00:19:39.446 --> 00:19:46.864
So what intelligence it has within a little cell, that is at the tip of the root.

00:19:46.971 --> 00:19:49.218
And this is what we have to know,

00:19:49.298 --> 00:19:55.752
that we have that [unclear/shraddha], which is the tip of the root, you can say.

00:19:55.833 --> 00:20:01.317
We should just make [unclear] and how to move,

00:20:01.404 --> 00:20:05.270
because nature is all within the control of this Power.

00:20:05.351 --> 00:20:08.258
So it doesn’t bother – it is not bothered about anything,

00:20:08.338 --> 00:20:11.016
[unclear/it just knows, that’s all] how this Power works.

00:20:11.097 --> 00:20:15.969
Only we have to figure, to decide: only we have to figure out, to decide.

00:20:16.049 --> 00:20:22.549
And this is the day when we have to decide that, whatever is good for the whole humanity,

00:20:22.629 --> 00:20:29.064
it should be done through us – you are an instrument, but the Power is in you.

00:20:29.145 --> 00:20:35.205
You just surrender yourself entirely to this 
divine Power [unclear/it will all be all right.].

00:20:35.285 --> 00:20:38.606
So today is a special work you have to do: we are few people here, I know

00:20:38.686 --> 00:20:45.721
but if you all decide this, it will all work out in a very, very beautiful manner.

00:20:46.228 --> 00:20:48.214
May God bless you.

00:21:01.380 --> 00:21:06.533
Yogi: We are very fortunate, Shri Mataji, that You have come.

00:21:06.614 --> 00:21:09.747
We are very fortunate You are here on this day in Bombay.

00:21:09.827 --> 00:21:15.852
Shri Mataji: Now it is for you to carry on, this little gathering to a big,

00:21:15.932 --> 00:21:22.603
you can call, a very big area, where people get enlightened

00:21:22.683 --> 00:21:29.289
and can receive the blessings of this all-pervading Power, which exists.

00:21:29.370 --> 00:21:32.045
I have done nothing, I should say, but one thing

00:21:32.125 --> 00:21:36.853
that, I have told people that this Power is available to everyone.

00:21:37.565 --> 00:21:43.302
Whether you call yourself anything, this Power is there, is available and can work.

00:21:43.383 --> 00:21:47.047
And the Kundalini is the one which connects you to this Power.

00:21:47.653 --> 00:21:51.532
That’s all – it is a very simple thing I have told you.

00:21:51.613 --> 00:21:58.414
But it has worked: it has worked as you know – for
thousands and thousands of people all over the world,

00:21:58.527 --> 00:22:02.306
because, you see, they never believed that there is such a Power.

00:22:02.387 --> 00:22:06.867
Even if they believed [unclear], it’s like half and half.

00:22:06.947 --> 00:22:10.080
But now when you feel it, it’s on your hands: that’s it.

00:22:10.161 --> 00:22:12.485
[unclear/ Just now, open your hands and see].

00:22:12.565 --> 00:22:18.574
You can feel it on your hands, on your fingertips and know what it is: it’s there.

00:22:18.654 --> 00:22:27.814
[unclear] or you can see the experience of that; just talking is not going to help you.

00:22:31.834 --> 00:22:35.242
[speaks aside to yogi: All right, we start.].

00:22:39.488 --> 00:22:42.490
So this is what is very, very important,

00:22:42.570 --> 00:22:47.448
that you have to have full faith in the all-pervading,

00:22:47.535 --> 00:22:55.146
that is God, is there – mentally, physically, emotionally – everything,

00:22:55.233 --> 00:23:00.258
and that is what will… that will cleanse you, that will cure you,

00:23:00.351 --> 00:23:06.236
that will give you all the blessings that you want.